{"type":null,"faqId":47351,"title":"如何升级手机？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{color:#333333;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=175731\" style=\"width:0.93680555in;height:0.43680555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">为防止手机内存中的用户数据（如：联系人、信息、通话记录等）在升级时被删除，建议升级前备份手机数据。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span class=\"s1\">在线升级：在线升级前，请连接移动网络或 WLAN。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s1\">进入“设置”界面，点击“系统更新 &gt; 检查更新”，检测到新版本后，根据屏幕提示完成升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span class=\"s1\">本地升级：进入</span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/downloads/index.htm%22 \\o %22 \"><span class=\"s1\">华为官网软件下载地址</span></a><span class=\"s1\">下载软件升级包，将软件包放入 dload 文件夹中，并将此文件夹放在 microSD 卡根目录下。然后将 microSD 卡插入手机。参考升级包中的升级指导完成升级。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":141,"faqType":"备份恢复与升级","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2918","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Backup-Restore-Update","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445219241000,"seriesProductName":"TIT-AL00,TIT-CL10,TIT-TL00","visitedTimes":598,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"手机升级","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}